text: cng klaw theid “thæcring phracea khxng chanth rng phæ paccay yangchiph kæ phu thi phraxngkh thrng prasngkh cak pwng baw khxng phraxngkh læa thrng hı khabkhæb kæ khea læa xan dı thi phwk cea bricakh cak sing dı k di phraxngkh ca thrng thdthæn man læa phraxngkh nan thrng pen phudi leis hæng brrda phu prathan paccay yangchiph
